Feature: Login

In order to perform successfull login
As a user
I want to enter correct username and password

Scenario Outline: In order to verify login to "facebook.com"
 		Given user navigates to facebook website
 		When user validates to homepage "title"
 		Then user entered "valid" username
 		And user entered "valid" password 
 		Then user "shouldbe" successfully logged in
 		
Examples :
|username	|password	|logintype	|
|valid		|valid		|should		|
|invalid	|invalid	|should not	|